Description: Rest on the flight into Egypt; in centre, the Virgin seated at the foot of a tree and turned towards right, holding the infant Christ in her arms, with St Joseph to right, seated and reading, see from behind; a round composition. c.1641 Etching
Producer name: Print made by: Stefano della Bella
Curator's comments: Dated c.1649 by De Vesme and c.1641 by Massar.
